{"type":null,"faqId":21875,"title":"我买了两台荣耀路由，如何级联上网？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in;}\n.p1{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.15763889in;margin-left:0.15763889in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.4861111in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<a name=\"storage_1_sec2_p1\"></a><span>两台荣耀路由可以通过有线或Wi-Fi级联后，基于华为智联特性将自动组成覆盖更广的 Wi-Fi 智联网络。下级的从路由器将自动同步主路由器的 Wi-Fi 名称和密码。用户手机在两个荣耀路由Wi-Fi 热点间移动时，智联网络将自动为用户手机选择信号最强的Wi-Fi热点，无需手动配置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">&gt;  </span><span class=\"s2\">方法一  网线直连：</span><a name=\"OLE_LINK2\"><span>先将第一台荣耀路由器配置好，保证其可以正常访问互联网</span></a><span>。然后用网线连接第二台荣耀路由的蓝色网口（WAN 口）和第一台荣耀路由的黄色网口（LAN 口），此时第二台荣耀路由的Hi灯将自动橙色快闪，停止闪烁时表明智联网组建完成。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">&gt;  </span><span class=\"s2\">方法二  Wi-Fi互联， 通过Hi 按键一键配对：</span><span>先将第一台荣耀路由器配置好，保证其可以正常访问互联网。然后将第二台荣耀路由接通电源并放在第一台荣耀路由1米范围内。当第一台荣耀路由的 Hi 灯开始橙灯慢闪时按下它的 Hi 按键，可以自动完成组网。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">&gt;  </span><span class=\"s2\">方法三  Wi-Fi互联，通过HiLink APP 智联界面添加新设备: </span><span>先将第一台荣耀路由器配置好，保证其可以正常访问互联网。然后将第二台荣耀接通电源。手机连接第一台荣耀路由的 Wi-Fi，打开 HiLink APP ，进入 HiLink 的“智联”添加第二台荣耀路由，可以自动完成组网。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5615","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1428048448000,"seriesProductName":"WS831-10","visitedTimes":119,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}